---
import BaseLayout from '@/components/layout/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Background and practice of Moe Qadan, a senior UX and frontend practitioner based in Los Angeles. UX engineering, design systems, frontend implementation, and AI-assisted product work across long-running platforms and independent product surfaces."
  keywords={[
    'Moe Qadan',
    'about',
    'UX engineer',
    'frontend engineer',
    'design engineer',
    'web experience',
    'design systems',
    'background',
    'creative technologist',
    'Los Angeles',
  ]}
>
  <div class="about">
    {/* Page atmosphere — soft accent glow at the top */}
    <div class="about__atmos" aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="about__atmos-glow"></span>
    </div>

    <header class="about__hero">
      <div class="container-site">
        <div class="about__sxn">
          <span class="about__sxn-num">01</span>
          <span class="about__sxn-label">Profile</span>
          <span class="about__sxn-rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="about__sxn-meta">Independent senior generalist</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="about__title">Moe Qadan.</h1>
        <p class="about__hero-sub">
          Senior UX and frontend practitioner based in Los Angeles. I
          do the parts of web work that usually get split across a
          team. Most days that's the seam where Figma, the codebase,
          the content model, the SEO graph, and the performance budget
          all have to agree.
        </p>

        <div class="about__id-strip">
          <a href="/contact" class="about__id-status" aria-label="Send a message">
            <span class="about__id-status-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            Send a message
          </a>
          <span class="about__id-sep" aria-hidden="true">/</span>
          <span class="about__id-loc">Los Angeles, CA</span>
          <span class="about__id-sep" aria-hidden="true">/</span>
          <a href="mailto:moe@qadan.co" class="about__id-mail">moe@qadan.co</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="container-site about__body">
      <div class="about__main">
        {/* What I'm best at */}
        <section class="about__section" data-reveal>
          <header class="about__sxn about__sxn--inner">
            <span class="about__sxn-num">02</span>
            <span class="about__sxn-label">What I'm best at</span>
            <span class="about__sxn-rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </header>
          <h2 class="about__h2">A few shapes the work tends to take.</h2>
          <ul class="about__bullets">
            <li><strong>Owning the whole web experience for a team that doesn't have a department for it.</strong> UX, design system, frontend, content architecture, SEO, performance, accessibility, all on one person.</li>
            <li><strong>Modernizing platforms that can't be rewritten.</strong> Long-running systems with traffic on them, opinions baked in, integrations the business depends on. The win is incremental, sequenced, and invisible when it lands.</li>
            <li><strong>Building component systems engineers actually use.</strong> Typed, documented, scoped, migrated to without flag days. Right now it's a 100+ component Razor partial library at MagTek; previously it was per-tenant CSS systems on InvestCloud's framework across more than 50 institutions.</li>
            <li><strong>Translating design intent into code at fidelity.</strong> Reading what the file is asking for, not just what it specifies, and closing the gaps a handoff doesn't see. Most production breakage lives in those gaps.</li>
            <li><strong>Shipping AI-assisted features without the buzzword tax.</strong> Prompts as system rather than scattered components. Schema-bound outputs. The model held as one stage in a pipeline. ChatOBD2 is the worked example.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        {/* Background */}
        <section class="about__section" data-reveal>
          <header class="about__sxn about__sxn--inner">
            <span class="about__sxn-num">03</span>
            <span class="about__sxn-label">Background</span>
            <span class="about__sxn-rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="about__sxn-meta">2018 to present</span>
          </header>

          <ol class="about__career">
            <li class="about__career-item about__career-item--current about__career-item--flagship">
              <span class="about__career-corner about__career-corner--tl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="about__career-corner about__career-corner--tr" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="about__career-corner about__career-corner--bl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="about__career-corner about__career-corner--br" aria-hidden="true"></span>

              <header class="about__career-head">
                <span class="about__career-status">
                  <span class="about__career-status-dot"></span>
                  Current
                </span>
                <h3 class="about__career-title">ChatOBD2</h3>
                <span class="about__career-period">2025 to present</span>
              </header>
              <p class="about__career-desc">
                Founder, sole designer and engineer. AI-native automotive
                diagnostics product I built end to end: mobile app,
                marketing site, developer portal, prompt pipeline. The
                design problem was translation. Vehicle data is messy and
                technical; the verdict has to be a single sentence the
                driver can act on.
              </p>
              <p class="about__career-stack">
                React Native (Expo) · TypeScript · Supabase · BLE ·
                Structured prompt pipeline · Next.js + Tailwind for the
                marketing site
              </p>
            </li>

            <li class="about__career-item about__career-item--current about__career-item--platform">
              <span class="about__career-corner about__career-corner--tl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="about__career-corner about__career-corner--tr" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="about__career-corner about__career-corner--bl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="about__career-corner about__career-corner--br" aria-hidden="true"></span>

              <header class="about__career-head">
                <span class="about__career-status">
                  <span class="about__career-status-dot"></span>
                  Current
                </span>
                <h3 class="about__career-title">MagTek</h3>
                <span class="about__career-period">Now</span>
              </header>
              <p class="about__career-desc">
                I lead the web experience across MagTek.com, Magensa, the
                hardware product line, the support portal, and the network
                of related properties built on the shared ASP.NET MVC
                substrate. The work is platform-level: a 100+ component
                Razor partial library, a CSS foundation rebuilt as design
                tokens, navigation grammar that travels, sequenced
                migrations that don't break production.
              </p>
              <p class="about__career-stack">
                ASP.NET MVC · C# · Razor · hand-authored CSS ·
                JavaScript · Bootstrap
              </p>
            </li>

            <li class="about__career-item about__career-item--product">
              <span class="about__career-corner about__career-corner--tl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="about__career-corner about__career-corner--tr" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="about__career-corner about__career-corner--bl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="about__career-corner about__career-corner--br" aria-hidden="true"></span>

              <header class="about__career-head">
                <span class="about__career-status about__career-status--past">Past</span>
                <h3 class="about__career-title">InvestCloud</h3>
                <span class="about__career-period">Earlier</span>
              </header>
              <p class="about__career-desc">
                Contributed to or led 0-to-production deploys for advisor
                and customer portals across <strong>50+ wealth-management and
                banking institutions</strong>: Chase, Cetera, Northwestern
                Mutual, Voya, Silicon Valley Bank, East West Bank, and
                many more. Multi-tenant frontend, per-institution branding,
                dense data layouts, and the discipline that comes from
                fifty deploys against the same substrate.
              </p>
              <p class="about__career-stack">
                CSS · proprietary CMS / component framework · Figma
                handoff translation
              </p>
            </li>
          </ol>
        </section>

        {/* How I think */}
        <section class="about__section" data-reveal>
          <header class="about__sxn about__sxn--inner">
            <span class="about__sxn-num">04</span>
            <span class="about__sxn-label">How I think about the work</span>
            <span class="about__sxn-rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </header>

          <ol class="about__list">
            <li>
              <strong>Read the constraints first.</strong> Long-running platforms
              have opinions about how they want to be changed. Listening
              to them is how the work survives.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Get the structure right early.</strong> Components,
              tokens, layout primitives, content models. When those are
              sound most decisions become cheap. When they aren't every
              decision is expensive.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Use AI where it earns its place.</strong> Code in
              Claude or Cursor when it's faster than typing. Visual
              exploration in Claude Design when a frame is faster than
              markup. Figma when precision matters.
            </li>
          </ol>

          <p class="about__para about__para--note">
            More on the workflow itself, including how AI fits into the
            build pipeline, lives on the
            <a href="/approach" class="about__inline-link">approach</a> page.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>

      {/* Right column aside */}
      <aside class="about__aside">
        <div class="about__card about__card--current">
          <span class="about__card-corner about__card-corner--tl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="about__card-corner about__card-corner--tr" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="about__card-corner about__card-corner--bl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="about__card-corner about__card-corner--br" aria-hidden="true"></span>

          <header class="about__card-head">
            <span class="about__card-num">05</span>
            <h3 class="about__card-title">Currently</h3>
          </header>

          <ul class="about__card-list">
            <li>
              <span class="about__card-key">Focus</span>
              <span class="about__card-val">UX + frontend as one job. Design systems. AI-native product work. Long-running platforms.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="about__card-key">Building</span>
              <span class="about__card-val about__card-val--building">
                <a href="/work/chatobd2" class="about__card-pill about__card-pill--flagship">
                  <span class="about__card-pill-dot"></span>
                  ChatOBD2
                </a>
                <a href="/work/magtek-platform" class="about__card-pill about__card-pill--platform">
                  <span class="about__card-pill-dot"></span>
                  MagTek
                </a>
              </span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="about__card-key">Stack</span>
              <span class="about__card-val">TypeScript · React · React Native · Astro · ASP.NET MVC · C# · Razor · hand-authored CSS</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="about__card-key">Based in</span>
              <span class="about__card-val">Los Angeles, California</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="about__card about__card--reach">
          <span class="about__card-corner about__card-corner--tl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="about__card-corner about__card-corner--tr" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="about__card-corner about__card-corner--bl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="about__card-corner about__card-corner--br" aria-hidden="true"></span>

          <header class="about__card-head">
            <span class="about__card-num">06</span>
            <h3 class="about__card-title">Reach out</h3>
          </header>
          <p class="about__card-note">
            Project questions, design or engineering conversations. Replies within a day.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="about__card-cta">
            Get in touch
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    position: relative;
  }

  /* Atmospheric glow at top of page */
  .about__atmos {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 600px;
    pointer-events: none;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about__atmos-glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: -180px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 1100px;
    height: 540px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 50% at 50% 50%, var(--color-accent-muted), transparent 70%);
    filter: blur(28px);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .about__hero {
    position: relative;
    padding-top: calc(60px + var(--space-10));
    padding-bottom: var(--space-10);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about__hero {
      padding-top: calc(64px + var(--space-16));
      padding-bottom: var(--space-12);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
    }
  }

  /* Shared section-head pattern */
  .about__sxn {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .about__sxn--inner {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .about__sxn-num {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 22px;
    padding: 0 7px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background-color: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .about__sxn-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .about__sxn-rule {
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--color-border), transparent);
    min-width: 32px;
  }

  .about__sxn-meta {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .about__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(48px, 11vw, 96px);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    line-height: 1.02;
    color: var(--color-text);
    max-width: 18ch;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .about__hero-sub {
    font-size: clamp(16px, 1.7vw, 19px);
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 62ch;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  /* Identity strip below the intro */
  .about__id-strip {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px 14px;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
    padding-top: var(--space-5);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
  }

  .about__id-status {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 7px;
    padding: 4px 11px 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--color-text);
    background-color: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background-color 150ms, border-color 150ms, color 150ms;
  }

  .about__id-status:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    background-color: var(--color-accent-dim);
  }

  .about__id-status-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--color-text-subtle);
    transition: background-color 150ms;
  }

  .about__id-status:hover .about__id-status-dot {
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  @keyframes about-status-pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 0.7; transform: scale(0.85); }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .about__career-status-dot { animation: none; }
  }

  .about__id-sep {
    color: var(--color-border-strong);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
  }

  .about__id-loc {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .about__id-mail {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: var(--color-border);
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    transition: color 150ms, text-decoration-color 150ms;
  }

  .about__id-mail:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  /* Body grid */
  .about__body {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-10);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about__body {
      gap: var(--space-12);
      padding-bottom: var(--space-24);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .about__body {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 340px;
      gap: var(--space-16);
      align-items: start;
    }
  }

  .about__main {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-12);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about__main {
      gap: var(--space-16);
    }
  }

  .about__section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .about__h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(26px, 3vw, 36px);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.15;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    max-width: 28ch;
  }

  .about__para {
    font-size: clamp(15px, 1.5vw, 17px);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .about__para--note {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
    line-height: 1.65;
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background-color: var(--color-bg-muted);
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin-top: var(--space-5);
  }

  .about__inline-link {
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: var(--color-border);
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    transition: color 150ms, text-decoration-color 150ms;
  }

  .about__inline-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .about__bullets {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-6);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    max-width: 64ch;
  }

  .about__bullets li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 24px;
    font-size: clamp(15px, 1.5vw, 17px);
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .about__bullets li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.7em;
    width: 12px;
    height: 1px;
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .about__bullets strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Career timeline — each card carries its project accent */
  .about__career {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-5);
  }

  .about__career-item {
    --pc-accent: var(--color-text-subtle);
    --pc-accent-rgb: 113, 113, 122;
    position: relative;
    padding: var(--space-6);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-bg-elevated), var(--color-bg-muted));
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 280ms, box-shadow 280ms, transform 280ms var(--ease-out);
  }

  .about__career-item--flagship {
    --pc-accent: var(--color-accent);
    --pc-accent-rgb: var(--project-flagship-rgb);
  }
  .about__career-item--platform {
    --pc-accent-rgb: var(--project-platform-rgb);
    --pc-accent: rgb(var(--project-platform-rgb));
  }
  .about__career-item--product {
    --pc-accent-rgb: var(--project-product-rgb);
    --pc-accent: rgb(var(--project-product-rgb));
  }

  .about__career-item::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 80% at 100% 0%, rgba(var(--pc-accent-rgb), 0.10), transparent 55%);
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 320ms var(--ease-out);
  }

  .about__career-item--current::before {
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .about__career-item:hover {
    border-color: rgba(var(--pc-accent-rgb), 0.4);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card-hover);
  }

  .about__career-item:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .about__career-item--current {
    border-color: rgba(var(--pc-accent-rgb), 0.35);
  }

  @media (min-width: 600px) {
    .about__career-item {
      padding: var(--space-7) var(--space-8);
    }
  }

  /* Corner crosshairs */
  .about__career-corner {
    position: absolute;
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-text-subtle);
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0.3;
    transition: opacity 240ms, border-color 240ms;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .about__career-item:hover .about__career-corner {
    opacity: 1;
    border-color: var(--pc-accent);
  }

  .about__career-corner--tl { top: 8px; left: 8px; border-right: none; border-bottom: none; }
  .about__career-corner--tr { top: 8px; right: 8px; border-left: none; border-bottom: none; }
  .about__career-corner--bl { bottom: 8px; left: 8px; border-right: none; border-top: none; }
  .about__career-corner--br { bottom: 8px; right: 8px; border-left: none; border-top: none; }

  .about__career-head {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .about__career-status {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--pc-accent);
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    background-color: rgba(var(--pc-accent-rgb), 0.12);
